{"tid":395733,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【飲食經驗】red rice原來會幫人篤檸檬","createTime":"2017-09-11T05:12:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-11T05:30:11.000Z","uid":143795,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9d1fee842cd8a6484e8c720ffe6f922467ffeae0","tid":395733,"uid":143795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T05:12:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/11/130128_db513d8671a03b5ce650a819f0a904c9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F11%2F130128_db513d8671a03b5ce650a819f0a904c9.jpg&h=9023bdd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n琴日同fd去慈雲山間red rice食飯,我個fd叫左凍檸茶,黎到個陣杯檸檬茶喲檸檬好似俾人篤過,伸要啲檸檬冇晒味,我個fd就諗住叫佢俾多片檸檬就算,個店員叫極都吾應,仲要我講都未講已經黑晒面,佢就話我地不嬲都會幫人篤,我就成頭問號？？？？？？？<br />\n原來會幫人篤架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我想問問各位巴絲去食呢間啲檸檬都會幫人篤？？？？"},{"pid":"011a0b1df937a39c322983b907a84505c8fb2704","tid":395733,"uid":27381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T05:13:45.000Z","msg":"服侍埋你又唔鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"109b27423e7c200d1756490bc6a9d05aedf83549","tid":395733,"uid":20653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T05:15:56.000Z","msg":"吾你老母"},{"pid":"3f546629c2c02d04a5a19e31664e559a66170466","tid":395733,"uid":66111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T05:20:41.000Z","msg":"上一手飲過加水加糖漿"},{"pid":"1474c9377e1240d3f409f78facb6aebc026fc7be","tid":395733,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T05:23:05.000Z","msg":"吾你老母<br />\n你呢d社會垃圾唔俾坑渠水你飲算偷笑"},{"pid":"c140c9252ad5644462486b69884fa8dc73aec623","tid":395733,"uid":40925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T05:27:48.000Z","msg":"環保檸檬"},{"pid":"7718daa3173b055175ff1d8b94ee0375c60b15fd","tid":395733,"uid":41325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-